---
import '../../style.css';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Not That Deep</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A small tool for right-sizing your reaction." />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,400;9..40,500;9..40,600;9..40,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body data-mode="dismiss">
    <main>
      <header class="site-header"><a class="brand" href="#" aria-label="Not That Deep home">NOT<br />THAT<br /><em>DEEP</em></a><p class="tagline">A reaction-sizing service<br />for the online and internal worlds.</p></header>
      <nav class="mode-switch" aria-label="Choose a mode"><button class="mode active" data-mode="dismiss" type="button"><span>01</span> Dismiss it</button><button class="mode" data-mode="reset" type="button"><span>02</span> Reset</button></nav>
      <section class="panel dismiss-panel" id="dismiss-panel"><div class="eyebrow">Office of Proportion &amp; Perspective</div><h1>Is this worth<br />your afternoon?</h1><p class="intro">Submit the incident for a completely impartial official ruling.</p><label class="sr-only" for="incident">What happened?</label><textarea id="incident" maxlength="220" placeholder="e.g. They replied “interesting” to my very normal post"></textarea><div class="form-row"><span class="character-count"><b id="count">0</b> / 220</span><button id="rule-button" class="primary-button" type="button">Issue ruling <span>→</span></button></div>
        <article class="ruling hidden" id="ruling" aria-live="polite"><div class="ruling-topline"><span>CASE FILE <b id="case-number">NTD–000</b></span><span>STATUS: CLOSED</span></div><div class="ruling-body"><p class="ruling-label">Official finding</p><h2 id="ruling-title">Insufficient grounds for a spiral.</h2><p id="ruling-copy"></p></div><div class="stamp">NOT<br />THAT<br />DEEP</div><footer><span>No further correspondence required.</span><span>Filed today</span></footer><div class="ruling-actions"><button id="share-ruling" type="button">Share ruling</button><button id="download-ruling" type="button">Save image</button></div></article>
      </section>
      <section class="panel reset-panel hidden" id="reset-panel"><div class="reset-heading"><div class="eyebrow">A small interruption</div><h1>Let’s make this<br />a little quieter.</h1><p>This won’t solve everything. It can help make room for the next minute.</p></div><label for="spiral">What’s looping? <small>Optional</small></label><input id="spiral" type="text" maxlength="180" placeholder="You can name it, or leave this blank." /><div class="technique-picker" role="group" aria-label="Choose a grounding technique"><button class="technique selected" data-technique="breathing" type="button">Paced breathing</button><button class="technique" data-technique="senses" type="button">5–4–3–2–1 senses</button><button class="technique" data-technique="defusion" type="button">A little distance</button><button class="technique" data-technique="category" type="button">Name ten things</button></div><button class="start-reset" id="start-reset" type="button">Start this one <span>→</span></button>
        <section class="exercise hidden" id="exercise" aria-live="polite"><div class="exercise-meta"><span id="exercise-type">PACED BREATHING</span><button id="choose-another" type="button">Choose another</button></div><div id="exercise-content"></div><div class="close-message hidden" id="close-message"><span class="close-mark">✓</span><div><strong>That was a real feeling.</strong><p id="close-copy">You gave it a little less of the whole room. That counts.</p></div></div></section><p class="crisis-line">If this feels like more than a passing spiral, you deserve more support. In the U.S. or Canada, call or text <a href="https://988lifeline.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">988</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <script src="../../app.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
